NFR-01: Performance

Description:
The system shall provide fast and efficient responses to user actions.

Acceptance Criteria:

System response time shall be within 3 seconds for normal operations

Multiple users can access the system simultaneously without performance degradation

NFR-02: Security

Description:
The system shall ensure secure access and protect sensitive data.

Acceptance Criteria:

User authentication is mandatory for system access

Passwords are stored securely

Unauthorized access attempts are denied

NFR-03: Usability

Description:
The system shall be easy to use for all categories of users.

Acceptance Criteria:

User interface is simple and intuitive

Users can perform basic tasks without training

Clear error messages are displayed

NFR-04: Reliability & Availability

Description:
The system shall operate reliably with minimal downtime.

Acceptance Criteria:

System availability of at least 99% during operational hours

Data is preserved during system failures

System recovers without data loss
